title: Check your driving test appointment details

heading_context: Check your driving test appointment details
chunks.html_content:
Use this service to check your driving test appointment details if you’ve lost or deleted your email confirmation. You can check the:

  • date and time of your driving test
  • address of the driving test centre

You do not need to take your booking confirmation to your driving test.

This service is available from 6am to 11:40pm.

You need your:

  • UK driving licence number
  • theory test pass certificate number (from the letter you got when you passed your theory test) or your driving test reference number if you have it
